The paper discusses the technical landscape of HLAI, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed alternative techniques involve scenario mapping and expert opinion elicitation, which are related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC), cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG).
